[SPEAKER_02] a ja bi trebao znao šta se događa u suvozačevo glavi.

1350
00:44:40,300 --> 00:44:44,340
[SPEAKER_02] Do sad sam recimo, za cijeli podcast pričam o vozaču, o autu,

1351
00:44:44,599 --> 00:44:46,780
[SPEAKER_02] uo neće mu, znači nema ništa u mišićima,

1352
00:44:46,780 --> 00:44:48,139
[SPEAKER_02] nego ja tu moram napraviti red.

1353
00:44:48,139 --> 00:44:51,340
[SPEAKER_02] Tako suvozač mora kod sebe napraviti red.

1354
00:44:51,340 --> 00:44:52,780
[SPEAKER_02] I to je jedan veliki problem.

1355
00:44:52,780 --> 00:44:55,400
[SPEAKER_02] Zato što baš na reliju ja ne radim sam sa sobom,

1356
00:44:55,400 --> 00:44:57,760
[SPEAKER_02] nego ja se suvozačem prolazim stazu

1357
00:44:57,760 --> 00:45:00,000
[SPEAKER_02] i nas dvojca zapisujemo stazu.

1358
00:45:00,000 --> 00:45:01,340
[SPEAKER_02] Ja govorim ljevi, dva, desni, tri.

1359
00:45:01,340 --> 00:45:02,940
[SPEAKER_02] Ja se procijenjujem kakvi su to zavoji.

1360
00:45:02,940 --> 00:45:07,119
[SPEAKER_02] I ako je jedan zavoj fulom na reliju,

1361
00:45:07,119 --> 00:45:08,840
[SPEAKER_02] ja na tom zavoju ću izletit van.

1362
00:45:08,840 --> 00:45:11,460
[SPEAKER_02] Znači ako taj zavoj nije, evo sad karikiram,

1363
00:45:11,719 --> 00:45:13,480
[SPEAKER_02] ljevi pet, nego ljevi pet minus.

1364
00:45:13,480 --> 00:45:16,219
[SPEAKER_02] I ako idem na onaj totalni ful,

1365
00:45:16,219 --> 00:45:18,179
[SPEAKER_02] ja budem na tom zavoju spalio van.

1366
00:45:18,179 --> 00:45:20,139
[SPEAKER_02] Ili ako nisam vidio da bi na tom zavoju

1367
00:45:20,139 --> 00:45:21,380
[SPEAKER_02] moglo biti promjena.

1368
00:45:21,380 --> 00:45:24,099
[SPEAKER_02] Promjene su u principu kao šoder.

1369
00:45:24,500 --> 00:45:27,179
[SPEAKER_02] Ako nisam vidio da taj zavoj recimo nema rinzol,

1370
00:45:27,179 --> 00:45:29,420
[SPEAKER_02] nego ima trave malo sa strane.

1371
00:45:29,420 --> 00:45:32,280
[SPEAKER_02] I ako padne kiša, dan ranije,

1372
00:45:32,280 --> 00:45:33,920
[SPEAKER_02] ta trava postane vlažna

1373
00:45:33,920 --> 00:45:35,780
[SPEAKER_02] i meni od jedan put ide mokra zemlja.

1374
00:45:35,780 --> 00:45:38,039
[SPEAKER_02] I ti voziš po suhom asfaltu, sve je super,

1375
00:45:38,039 --> 00:45:39,420
[SPEAKER_02] od jedan put naletiš na mokru zemlju

1376
00:45:39,420 --> 00:45:40,460
[SPEAKER_02] i izletiš van.

1377
00:45:40,539 --> 00:45:42,519
[SPEAKER_02] To su recimo situacije

1378
00:45:42,519 --> 00:45:44,000
[SPEAKER_02] gdje ti može pomoći jako suvozač.

1379
00:45:44,000 --> 00:45:45,699
[SPEAKER_02] Zašto su dvije glave uvijek pametnije.

1380
00:45:45,699 --> 00:45:48,079
[SPEAKER_02] Međutim, suvozač mora na tom treningu,

1381
00:45:48,079 --> 00:45:49,079
[SPEAKER_02] kad smo mi opušteni,

1382
00:45:49,079 --> 00:45:50,539
[SPEAKER_02] ne da nam se, itd., itd.,

1383
00:45:50,539 --> 00:45:53,679
[SPEAKER_02] mora otvoriti isto tako oči

1384
00:45:53,679 --> 00:45:56,119
[SPEAKER_02] i mora biti dio tima.

1385
00:45:56,119 --> 00:45:58,980
[SPEAKER_02] A to je za suvozače ponekad jako, jako teško.

1386
00:45:58,980 --> 00:46:00,860
[SPEAKER_02] Suvozač je totalno drugačija,

1387
00:46:00,860 --> 00:46:02,539
[SPEAKER_02] drugačija osoba od vlazača.

1388
00:46:02,539 --> 00:46:03,639
[SPEAKER_02] Potpuno se drugačija osoba.

1389
00:46:03,639 --> 00:46:06,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ne moraju dvije osobe biti iste,

1390
00:46:06,320 --> 00:46:07,179
[SPEAKER_01] ni čak ni slične,

1391
00:46:07,179 --> 00:46:07,900
[SPEAKER_01] nego je čak poželjne.

1392
00:46:07,900 --> 00:46:09,480
[SPEAKER_02] Govora, ja imam istu osobu koju ja,

1393
00:46:09,480 --> 00:46:10,420
[SPEAKER_02] mi ćemo se pobiti.

1394
00:46:10,420 --> 00:46:11,239
[SPEAKER_02] Ne mu bilo dobro.

1395
00:46:11,239 --> 00:46:13,980
[SPEAKER_01] To mogu zamisliti čak,

1396
00:46:13,980 --> 00:46:16,659
[SPEAKER_01] ali kako bi to komunikacija onda trebala biti?

1397
00:46:16,659 --> 00:46:17,559
[SPEAKER_01] Je li to direktna?

1398
00:46:17,559 --> 00:46:18,800
[SPEAKER_01] Deranje, uglavnom deranje.

1399
00:46:18,800 --> 00:46:20,599
[SPEAKER_02] Deramo se jedana druga,

1400
00:46:20,599 --> 00:46:22,400
[SPEAKER_02] praštamo ponekad.

1401
00:46:22,400 --> 00:46:23,400
[SPEAKER_02] Dobro, ponekad.

1402
00:46:23,480 --> 00:46:26,239
[SPEAKER_02] Ponekad ostavim me na miru.

1403
00:46:26,239 --> 00:46:29,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ok, ali meni se to čini da je to vrlo iskrena

1404
00:46:29,340 --> 00:46:30,880
[SPEAKER_01] i vrlo direktna komunikacija.

1405
00:46:30,880 --> 00:46:32,059
[SPEAKER_01] Da.

1406
00:46:32,059 --> 00:46:33,860
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko su ljudi spremni na to?

1407
00:46:33,860 --> 00:46:37,860
[SPEAKER_02] Nisu, zato što biti suvozač na naticanju

1408
00:46:37,860 --> 00:46:39,440
[SPEAKER_02] neko uzima u obzir da je to

1409
00:46:39,440 --> 00:46:41,480
[SPEAKER_02] jeden kokic i gledam kako ti voziš

1410
00:46:41,480 --> 00:46:42,340
[SPEAKER_02] i uživam u tome.

1411
00:46:42,340 --> 00:46:44,519
[SPEAKER_02] Iz prvog reda u kinu.

1412
00:46:44,519 --> 00:46:45,179
[SPEAKER_02] Niti govora.

1413
00:46:45,179 --> 00:46:46,880
[SPEAKER_02] Nego mi smo skupa,

1414
00:46:46,880 --> 00:46:48,739
[SPEAKER_02] imamo zajednu glavu u loncu

1415
00:46:48,739 --> 00:46:51,340
[SPEAKER_02] i ja od suvozača imam zapravo,

1416
00:46:51,340 --> 00:46:53,340
[SPEAKER_02] ovisi sad, zali je suvozač na reliju

1417
00:46:53,340 --> 00:46:54,039
[SPEAKER_02] ili na dakru.

1418
00:46:54,039 --> 00:46:56,300
[SPEAKER_02] Na to su opet dvije različite uloge.

1419
00:46:56,300 --> 00:47:01,199
[SPEAKER_02] Ja od te osobe zapravo očekujem svoj maksimum.

1420
00:47:01,199 --> 00:47:03,699
[SPEAKER_02] A biti suvozač i dati svoj maksimum

1421
00:47:03,699 --> 00:47:05,780
[SPEAKER_02] je onak poprlično teško

1422
00:47:05,780 --> 00:47:07,579
[SPEAKER_02] zato što njemu adrenalin nije na 170.

1423
00:47:07,579 --> 00:47:09,699
[SPEAKER_02] On mora biti mrvicu samosmireniji

1424
00:47:09,699 --> 00:47:10,900
[SPEAKER_02] i mora biti pametniji.

1425
00:47:10,900 --> 00:47:13,400
[SPEAKER_02] I suvozač uđe u tu svoju zonu.

1426
00:47:13,400 --> 00:47:14,360
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ne znam koja je ona.

1427
00:47:14,760 --> 00:47:16,119
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ne znam koja je ona.

1428
00:47:16,119 --> 00:47:17,480
[SPEAKER_02] Bio jesan suvozač.

1429
00:47:17,480 --> 00:47:19,239
[SPEAKER_02] Znao sam se kasniti onak,

1430
00:47:19,239 --> 00:47:20,980
[SPEAKER_02] fulom zaoje, pročitam zaoje.

1431
00:47:20,980 --> 00:47:23,119
[SPEAKER_02] Vidio sam stvarno da tu ne funkcioniram dobro.

1432
00:47:23,119 --> 00:47:25,679
[SPEAKER_02] Postoje ljudi koji samo u tome dobro funkcioniraju.

1433
00:47:25,679 --> 00:47:27,400
[SPEAKER_02] Biti suvozač treba ti nekoliko

1434
00:47:27,400 --> 00:47:35,980
[SPEAKER_02] značajke, urednost u životu i u glavi.

1435
00:47:35,980 --> 00:47:38,920
[SPEAKER_02] Uredno pisati, ima dobar rukopis.

1436
00:47:38,920 --> 00:47:42,019
[SPEAKER_02] Skužiti na koji način da uđeš u zonu

1437
00:47:42,019 --> 00:47:45,260
[SPEAKER_02] sa ljevom nogom, ljev, dva, desni, tri,

1438
00:47:45,260 --> 00:47:46,179
[SPEAKER_02] da nikad ne pogriješi.

1439
00:47:46,179 --> 00:47:49,800
[SPEAKER_02] To neko može, neko griješi cijelo vrijeme,

1440
00:47:49,800 --> 00:47:50,579
[SPEAKER_02] kao recimo ja.

1441
00:47:50,579 --> 00:47:54,699
[SPEAKER_02] I zaista to volje ti htjeti.

1442
00:47:54,699 --> 00:47:57,300
[SPEAKER_02] Obožavati to da sjedneš na taj desni sic.

1443
00:47:58,099 --> 00:48:00,440
[SPEAKER_02] Jer ako suvozač ima ambiciju da bude vozač,

1444
00:48:00,440 --> 00:48:02,880
[SPEAKER_02] onda ta frustracija izlazi van za

1445
00:48:02,880 --> 00:48:04,699
[SPEAKER_02] pet, četiri, tri, dva i jedan.

1446
00:48:04,699 --> 00:48:06,780
[SPEAKER_02] I kad ta frustracija, ja bih to bolje napravila,

1447
00:48:06,780 --> 00:48:08,019
[SPEAKER_02] ti to ne znaš, ti ovako,

1448
00:48:08,019 --> 00:48:10,360
[SPEAKER_02] ok, budem se uzirati nekog drugoga,

1449
00:48:10,360 --> 00:48:12,239
[SPEAKER_02] jer mi niko ne treba da mi soli pamet,

1450
00:48:12,239 --> 00:48:13,599
[SPEAKER_02] nego mi treba da mi neko pomogne

1451
00:48:13,599 --> 00:48:14,980
[SPEAKER_02] kada ja izvučem maksimum.

1452
00:48:14,980 --> 00:48:17,179
[SPEAKER_02] I onda ako meni neko počne soliti pamet,

1453
00:48:17,179 --> 00:48:19,280
[SPEAKER_02] rekao, ok, ili mi pomozi,

1454
00:48:19,280 --> 00:48:20,559
[SPEAKER_02] ili me nemoj frustrirati.

1455
00:48:20,559 --> 00:48:23,079
[SPEAKER_02] Znači suvozač je taj koji mora isto psihički

1456
00:48:23,079 --> 00:48:25,360
[SPEAKER_02] ocijeniti vozača i vidjeti na koji način

1457
00:48:25,360 --> 00:48:26,780
[SPEAKER_02] da mu pomogne, ako mu želi pomoć,

1458
00:48:26,780 --> 00:48:28,460
[SPEAKER_02] jer suvozač jako može vozač u odmah.

1459
00:48:28,460 --> 00:48:31,219
[SPEAKER_01] Jel više voleš sam biti ili u timu?

1460
00:48:31,219 --> 00:48:34,900
[SPEAKER_02] Kad je čovjek sam, onda imaš nejakav svoj red,

1461
00:48:34,900 --> 00:48:35,980
[SPEAKER_02] znaš što možeš očekivati.

1462
00:48:35,980 --> 00:48:38,179
[SPEAKER_02] Kada si u timu, odnosno vozač i suvozač,

1463
00:48:38,179 --> 00:48:42,920
[SPEAKER_02] onda ponekad, onda to može ponekad biti naporno.

1464
00:48:42,920 --> 00:48:45,320
[SPEAKER_02] Može biti ponekad jako, jako naporno.

1465
00:48:45,320 --> 00:48:47,199
[SPEAKER_02] Ako imaš osobu sa kojom,

1466
00:48:47,900 --> 00:48:49,739
[SPEAKER_02] ovisi kak sa kim čovjek klikne, jel?

1467
00:48:49,739 --> 00:48:51,239
[SPEAKER_02] Da, jasno, da.

1468
00:48:51,239 --> 00:48:51,900
[SPEAKER_02] Brlo jednostavno.

1469
00:48:51,900 --> 00:48:53,079
[SPEAKER_02] Ako mene neko razumije,

1470
00:48:53,079 --> 00:48:56,559
[SPEAKER_02] postoje suvozači koji,

1471
00:48:56,559 --> 00:48:57,840
[SPEAKER_02] mislim, imao sam raznih suvozača.

1472
00:48:57,840 --> 00:48:59,780
[SPEAKER_02] I slagao sam se i nisam se slagao.

1473
00:48:59,780 --> 00:49:01,739
[SPEAKER_02] Savršenog nisam našao.

1474
00:49:01,739 --> 00:49:04,420
[SPEAKER_02] Savršenog nisam našao ko može biti sa mnom

1475
00:49:04,420 --> 00:49:06,179
[SPEAKER_02] i ko mene može ovoga prožvakati.

1476
00:49:06,179 --> 00:49:10,519
[SPEAKER_02] Jer ja, kad sam pod adenalinom pod 170,

1477
00:49:12,039 --> 00:49:12,820
[SPEAKER_02] Ana, kada je to?

1478
00:49:12,820 --> 00:49:13,679
[SPEAKER_02] Da je ovdje tamo, brzo.

1479
00:49:13,679 --> 00:49:14,440
[SPEAKER_02] Jer mi nemamo vremena.

1480
00:49:14,440 --> 00:49:15,519
[SPEAKER_02] Mi sad kasnimo negdje.

1481
00:49:15,519 --> 00:49:17,679
[SPEAKER_02] I mi sad moramo promijeniti gumu

1482
00:49:17,679 --> 00:49:19,139
[SPEAKER_02] za dve minute.

1483
00:49:19,139 --> 00:49:21,420
[SPEAKER_02] E, a, znaš kje se na tebi htjela reći?

1484
00:49:21,420 --> 00:49:23,719
[SPEAKER_02] Ne zanima me, mijenje gumu.

1485
00:49:23,719 --> 00:49:25,719
[SPEAKER_02] I drugo, ne postoji.

1486
00:49:25,719 --> 00:49:27,400
[SPEAKER_02] I onda, kak je od mene sad uvredilo?

1487
00:49:27,400 --> 00:49:28,159
[SPEAKER_02] Zak je on sad to rekao?

1488
00:49:28,159 --> 00:49:30,320
[SPEAKER_01] Da, da, da, nemate se vremena baviti.

1489
00:49:30,320 --> 00:49:31,440
[SPEAKER_02] Mi sad ginemo.

1490
00:49:31,440 --> 00:49:34,119
[SPEAKER_02] I sad onaj koji shvaća, veli, na zapovjed.

1491
00:49:34,119 --> 00:49:35,059
[SPEAKER_02] Mi sad ginemo.

1492
00:49:35,059 --> 00:49:37,199
[SPEAKER_02] I onda poslije toga ćemo razgovarati.

1493
00:49:37,199 --> 00:49:40,500
[SPEAKER_02] A onaj kao, veli, ti uopće ne razmišljaš o mojim osjećajima.

1494
00:49:40,500 --> 00:49:40,920
[SPEAKER_02] Ne.

1495
00:49:40,920 --> 00:49:43,719
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ne razmišljam niti o sebi, niti o svojim osjećajima.

1496
00:49:43,719 --> 00:49:46,039
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam apsolutno sve podredio rezultatu.

1497
00:49:46,039 --> 00:49:48,380
[SPEAKER_02] I ako imaš suhozača koji to razumije,

1498
00:49:48,380 --> 00:49:49,900
[SPEAKER_02] da sve podređuje rezultatu,

1499
00:49:49,900 --> 00:49:52,199
[SPEAKER_02] a onda imaš suhozača.

1500
00:49:52,199 --> 00:49:54,800
[SPEAKER_02] E, uvijek se tu...

1501
00:49:54,800 --> 00:49:56,000
[SPEAKER_02] Pa daj mi malo postavi na miru.

1502
00:49:56,000 --> 00:49:57,679
[SPEAKER_02] Ja bi ovo, ja bi ovo ono...

1503
00:49:57,679 --> 00:49:59,480
[SPEAKER_01] A sad ide jedno intimno pitanje.

1504
00:49:59,480 --> 00:50:02,519
[SPEAKER_01] Kako se to reflektira na tvoje privatne odnose?

1505
00:50:02,519 --> 00:50:04,039
[SPEAKER_01] Jesi li nekad previše direktan?

1506
00:50:04,039 --> 00:50:06,519
[SPEAKER_01] Onda u privatnim odnosima pod izlikom

1507
00:50:06,519 --> 00:50:09,280
[SPEAKER_01] nema se vremena za biti fin i baviti se osjećajima

1508
00:50:09,280 --> 00:50:10,800
[SPEAKER_01] ili je to apsolutno rezervirano?

1509
00:50:10,800 --> 00:50:12,960
[SPEAKER_02] Pa nije. Mislim da je ovoga...

1510
00:50:12,960 --> 00:50:13,800
[SPEAKER_02] Vratiš se nazad.

1511
00:50:13,800 --> 00:50:15,719
[SPEAKER_02] U mozgu se vratiš nazad.

1512
00:50:15,719 --> 00:50:18,880
[SPEAKER_02] Jedna je osoba ta koja vozi u utrke,

1513
00:50:18,880 --> 00:50:20,800
[SPEAKER_02] ja sam tamo...

1514
00:50:20,800 --> 00:50:22,480
[SPEAKER_01] To je ono s kaciglom i glavom.

1515
00:50:22,480 --> 00:50:23,800
[SPEAKER_02] Da, da, ja maknem mozak.

1516
00:50:23,800 --> 00:50:24,880
[SPEAKER_02] Ja sam druga osoba.

1517
00:50:24,880 --> 00:50:25,840
[SPEAKER_02] Mene ljudi ne prepoznajem.

1518
00:50:25,920 --> 00:50:27,000
[SPEAKER_02] Šta se takav ono...

1519
00:50:27,000 --> 00:50:27,880
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ne znam...

1520
00:50:27,880 --> 00:50:28,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ja ne znam...

1521
00:50:28,559 --> 00:50:30,219
[SPEAKER_02] Prosti, ne znam ni ko si ti, gospođo.

1522
00:50:30,219 --> 00:50:31,559
[SPEAKER_02] Ne znam zašto je ovdje.

1523
00:50:31,559 --> 00:50:33,460
[SPEAKER_02] Ja imam samo jednu isključivu misiju.

1524
00:50:33,460 --> 00:50:35,039
[SPEAKER_02] Zato što je automobilizam sport.

1525
00:50:35,039 --> 00:50:37,059
[SPEAKER_02] Znači, moja misija je sad takva.

1526
00:50:37,059 --> 00:50:37,320
[SPEAKER_02] Šta je?

1527
00:50:37,320 --> 00:50:38,500
[SPEAKER_02] Problem je što ljudi dolaze

1528
00:50:38,500 --> 00:50:40,260
[SPEAKER_02] na utrku zabavljati se, ne?

1529
00:50:40,260 --> 00:50:41,179
[SPEAKER_02] Ej, dođe s pivom.

1530
00:50:41,179 --> 00:50:42,099
[SPEAKER_02] Ej, friendi, di si?

1531
00:50:42,099 --> 00:50:42,500
[SPEAKER_02] Mrš.

1532
00:50:42,500 --> 00:50:43,340
[SPEAKER_02] Makni se od mene.

1533
00:50:43,340 --> 00:50:43,719
[SPEAKER_02] Zašto?

1534
00:50:43,719 --> 00:50:45,619
[SPEAKER_02] Zato što ja se trenutno rješavam ovdje

1535
00:50:45,619 --> 00:50:46,960
[SPEAKER_02] pitanje svog života i smrti.

1536
00:50:46,960 --> 00:50:47,599
[SPEAKER_02] Nije smiješno.

1537
00:50:47,599 --> 00:50:50,280
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je jako smrš bila, ali dobro.

